Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.21,0:00:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深淵祭壇？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.38,0:00:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅看到的大概就是這個哞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.01,0:00:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅色的城堡和發光的圓環…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到過！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅色的城堡…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅色的城堡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去深淵祭壇後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉 你知道這地方在哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.99,0:00:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了哞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.70,0:00:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.12,0:00:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你認真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.42,0:00:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去那說不定能搞清菲莉雅的來歷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能傻呆在這
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也跟著去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.68,0:00:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:00:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不允許！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是就是！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.56,0:01:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你們在這裡等著好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.14,0:01:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總而言之 我不同意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再讓你父母擔心了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在聽嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.03,0:01:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅曼…奥托…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.86,0:01:15.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.74,0:01:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哞！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說只要到了深淵祭壇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅就會停止成長了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之所以會成長是因為菲莉雅的力量不斷溢出哞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溢出了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到深淵祭壇的泉水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以找到能填補溢出的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高濃度吉夫特礦源流眸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他地方可是見都見不到的哞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉夫特礦源流？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來莫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本沒抑制住菲莉雅的力量嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哞…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾 佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們 能陪我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不能放著菲莉雅不管啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子餓了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成長地這麼快 也難怪肚子會餓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:03:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成長…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死盯著看什麼呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？我沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人哞 明明就是一副禽獸的眼神哞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別…別瞎扯！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快看到村子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那吃點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:37.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是結婚典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相愛的兩個人相互結台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.32,0:04:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙先生真體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來就是我們要用的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以來撫養宗吾長大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為他是你的親兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這樣的男人上哪去找老婆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…沒這回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快讓開！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅曼！奥托！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰幹的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是宗吾他們！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是要去深淵祭壇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搶了我們的氣動車走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深淵祭壇？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻幫我準備好瓦洛夫R7
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後我會和父親大人說明的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從蜜蜂那裡送來了情報
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會立刻派當地的直屬部隊前去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物件已經離開了靛藍花園
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在向玻爾維亞區域前進
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如各位所見 幾乎是一條路直通過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們第一個落腳點估計就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫紅花園
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳音穿過新娘禮服來著吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳音結過婚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在試婚紗的時候逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直等不到王子及時出現來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快躲開！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能站起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扭到脚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像扭到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走不了路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儀式要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們沒有可以換的花童啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓大人來的話會壞了規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃琳娜 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩旅途中的你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡 本來就是我們的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這還是第一次當花童
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關係好的一對來做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更容易招來好運
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有好多情侶就這麼喜結良緣了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情侶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不介意吧 佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…隨隨便便說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我和宗吾又不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是朋友 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.86,0:08:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青任又那麼重大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這衣服也輕飄飄的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…菲莉雅來？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意哞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那來這邊吧 幫你調下衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定會很合身的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這可是重要的結婚典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果搞砸了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 之後只要拿著貢品走就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不做的話比較好？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會教你該怎麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請就當做是幫我們個忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的吧 佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為什麼會說出那種話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到紫紅花園還有多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大約兩小時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能讓新人得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我在加斯來之前就把他們收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來支援的懸浮機在還差3伽羅的地方遭到空襲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來還活著的只剩我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有動靜了 加斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜蜂發來了情報
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是紫紅花園
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是達德利的部隊先去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該出動了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼好玩的雙足機甲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能眼睜睜被别人搶走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我也有點想看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗博伊爾為什麼麽會盯上那群人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 和城裡的結婚典禮不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也稍微客氣點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃哞真好吃哞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳音？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃點嗎 很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅是不是也在吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在換衣服 不可能的哞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明她是肚子最餓的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你幫她拿過去吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.31,0:12:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起我這樣的女巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅跟你配多了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:13:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢 不像平時的你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳音？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不像平時的我 我自己都這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我搞不太懂 但是就是那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.01,0:13:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真合身 小菲莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 像公主一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說你好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛 是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那個人快樂的話 自己也會感到快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那個人悲傷的話 自己也會覺得悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概就是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些像伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都不准動！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.16,0:14:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只是在找人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不妨礙我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就不會傷害這個花園的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政府的雙足機甲？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍頭髪的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我們走一趟！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.01,0:14:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅怎麼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是軍事機密！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對象從教會後門逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,念相2號向院內西側展開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別讓她逃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哞！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哞！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哞！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哞！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是報告裡說的不明歸屬的雙足機甲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不會讓你們帶走菲莉雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特意給我們提供戰功還真是多謝了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚐嚐這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼他們會知道我們在這
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅 把那件衣服給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來引開他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.49,0:16:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就趁機往村外逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳音…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算抓住了我對他們也沒什麼用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳音 我愛你！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那個人快樂的話 自己也會感到快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加果那個人悲傷的話 自己也會覺得悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:16:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 菲莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳音？你很難過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.23,0:17:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅做錯了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜歡菲莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.07,0:17:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜歡佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找〜到〜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍頭髪的女人到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來根本不需要加斯的支援
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的對手是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳音！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開她！那是我的朋友！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命今雖然說是儘量不要傷害平民…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:17:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳音！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了 各位！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本人羅曼．瓦洛夫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賭上瓦洛夫家之名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前來營救新娘！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅曼好帥！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擺姿勢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去救菲莉雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是豬啊！打中菲莉雅怎麼辦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會從右邊攻過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是從上方？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:28.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃找這招！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦洛夫・旋轉風暴！。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦洛夫・究極超騎…啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有兩把刷子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是王牌機師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:19:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奪回目標！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威豹之陣！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩架一起過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚐嚐這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是現在！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.81,0:20:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,報告上說是格鬥戰專用機體…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別妨礙我結婚！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.79,0:20:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太不知趣了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下地獄吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:54.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全員撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧 佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.31,0:21:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 就像王子和公主一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.42,0:21:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搶在前頭的灰頭土臉被打了回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不喜歡什麼間諜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過大家身上的擔子都不輕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特務蜜蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.57,0:23:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人在途中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.19,0:23:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔手逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.78,0:23:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人心難料
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.32,0:23:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感情背後
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.16,0:23:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集「彗星・路西法」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫暖的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起來拿上通往冒險的車票哞！
